.TH CLICALC 1 "December 2025" "clicalc 1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
clicalc \- simple command-line calculator
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B clicalc
.I number1 operator number2
.SH DESCRIPTION
clicalc is a simple command-line calculator that performs
basic arithmetic operations on floating-point numbers.
.SH OPERATORS
.TP
.B +
Addition
.TP
.B -
Subtraction
.TP
.B '*'
Multiplication
.TP
.B /
Division
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
clicalc 3.5 + 2
.TP
clicalc 5 '*' 5
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
0
Success
.TP
1
Error (invalid input or operator)
.SH AUTHOR
Tim Heineken
